Package playn.core

Class Tile

java.lang.Object
playn.core.TileSource
playn.core.Tile
Direct Known Subclasses:
Texture
public abstract class Tile extends TileSource
Represents a square region of a texture. This makes it easy to render tiles from texture atlases.
